593
00:41:24,639 --> 00:41:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerojatno postoji spektar, zar ne?

594
00:41:27,119 --> 00:41:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije to tvrda plaćena zida ili ne, ne, puno freemium.

595
00:41:30,079 --> 00:41:30,639
[SPEAKER_01] I znate što mislim?

596
00:41:31,440 --> 00:41:32,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da možete, možda čak i faza.

597
00:41:33,119 --> 00:41:38,719
